<A NAME="presentation"></A>
<H2>Who is Unify</H2>
Unify Corporation develops, markets and supports advanced application 
development environments for the development, deployment and management of 
high-end, business-critical client/server and Web solutions. The Company's 
flagship product, 
<A HREF="/Product/vis-over.html">Unify VISION</A>, 
combines a powerful and scalable client/server 
architecture with a flexible and easy-to-use rapid application development 
technology. Its built-in VISION/Web technology also gives VISION the ability 
to automatically generate Java applets.

Please take a few minutes to view our self-running presentation, 
<A HREF="/Presentation/presindex.html">
	"Unify: Providing Solutions for the Internet Age".</A>
This overview of the Unify solution 
includes information about our customers, partners and products. Hear first 
hand what Unify customers and industry analysts think about our technology.
